
# Advanced Programming Pac-Man Project

**Student Name:** [Eray Ayyildiz]
**Student Number:** [s0243673]
**Course:** Advanced Programming 2025-2026  
**University:** University of Antwerp

## Project Description
This is a C++ implementation of Pac-Man using SFML, following strict architectural requirements including MVC pattern, separation of logic/representation, and multiple design patterns.

## Build Instructions
```bash
mkdir build && cd build
cmake ..
make
./Pac-Man

